ace height=\"80px\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"overview\" font_container=\"tag:h6|font_size:10px|text_align:center|color:%23627792\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" el_class=\"style1\"][vc_empty_space height=\"6px\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Expert IT services for the banking Industry\" font_container=\"tag:h3|text_align:center\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][vc_empty_space height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]Faced with increasing competition, banking and financial services organizations must move quickly to meet new customer, employee and industry demands while addressing complex regulatory mandates and heightened security threats.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>To attract and retain customers, they must provide new and more innovative ways to interact with financial services, from online banking and mobile apps, to contact centers, to a more modern in-branch experience.</li>\r\n 	<li>Anytime access to resources and flexible work options are critical for attracting and engaging the most skilled staff.</li>\r\n 	<li>As markets evolve and emerge, they need the agility to grow, shift markets, outsource, acquire and divest rapidly, with continuous innovation to stay at the leading edge of global competition.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nBehind all these initiatives are the systems and infrastructure powered by NanoSoft. With strengths in every discipline across the entire portfolio of financial IT—including storage area networking, compliance, security, disaster recovery planning and more—NanoSoft is your partner in building true enterprise grade IT environments.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"60px\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section full_width=\"stretch_row\" el_id=\"sectors\" css=\".vc_custom_1536554594373{padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;}\" el_class=\"gradient3\"][vc_row css_animation=\"none\"][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"Sectors\" font_container=\"tag:h6|font_size:10px|text_align:center|color:%23627792\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" el_class=\"style1\"][vc_empty_space height=\"6px\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"The industry sectors we served include\" font_container=\"tag:h3|text_align:center\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][vc_empty_space height=\"60px\"][iconlist icon_size=\"small\" class=\"columns-3 gap-50\"][iconlist_item type=\"image\" icon_image=\"1286\"]\r\n<h4>Retail banking</h4>\r\nEnable superior digital experiences, by modernizing legacy systems and leveraging APIs, DevOps, and FinTech partnership ecosystem.[/iconlist_item][iconlist_item type=\"image\" icon_image=\"1287\"]\r\n<h4>Cards and payments</h4>\r\nEnable simple, frictionless, and compliant payments experience, by leveraging open API, digital payments, blockchain, and analytics.[/iconlist_item][iconlist_item type=\"image\" icon_image=\"1288\"]\r\n<h4>Corporate Banking</h4>\r\nTransform your business to align to the future of the trade finance industry, by leveraging blockchain, cloud, automation, and analytics.[/iconlist_item][iconlist_item type=\"image\" icon_image=\"1289\"]\r\n<h4>Investment banking</h4>\r\nDrive operational efficiencies and improve experience, by bringing a domain-centric middle and back-office transformation approach.[/iconlist_item][iconlist_item type=\"image\" icon_image=\"1290\"]\r\n<h4>Custody and fund services</h4>\r\nAdopt a platform-led approach, to drive automation and reduce costs, by consuming services in an as-a-service model.[/iconlist_item][iconlist_item type=\"image\" icon_image=\"1291\"]\r\n<h4>Risk and compliance</h4>\r\nGain competitive advantage from risk &amp; compliance efforts, with risk reporting, AML transformation, and product partners.[/iconlist_item][/iconlist][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section full_width=\"stretch_row\" css_animation=\"none\" el_id=\"benefits\" css=\".vc_custom_1536547449996{padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 80px !important;background-color: #231834 !important;}\"][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/12\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"5/6\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Benefits to bank on\" font_container=\"tag:h6|font_size:10px|text_align:center|color:%231dc2ef\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" el_class=\"style1\"][vc_empty_space height=\"6px\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Our clients are able to increase end-user productivity without sacrificing usability.\" font_container=\"tag:h3|text_align:center|color:%23ffffff\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][vc_empty_space height=\"60px\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/12\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css_animation=\"none\"][vc_column][iconlist][iconlist_item type=\"image\" class=\"aligncenter shadow wpb_animate_when_almost_visible fadeIn delay-1\" css=\".vc_custom_1540521637144{padding-right: 10% !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;padding-left: 10% !important;background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.05) !important;*background-color: rgb(255,255,255) !important;border-radius: 5px !important;}\"]\r\n<h6><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Business Agility</span></h6>\r\n<span style=\"color: #9b9aad;\">Business growth and seasonal flexibility are easily scaled as our banking IT services adapt to the client\'s needs allowing them to easily add and remove users without a headache.</span>[/iconlist_item][iconlist_item type=\"image\" class=\"aligncenter shadow wpb_animate_when_almost_visible fadeIn delay-2\" css=\".vc_custom_1540521646901{padding-right: 10% !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;padding-left: 10% !important;background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.05) !important;*background-color: rgb(255,255,255) !important;border-radius: 5px !important;}\"]\r\n<h6><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Security and compliance</span></h6>\r\n<span style=\"color: #9b9aad;\">Our clients are able to control business sensitive data and adhere to compliance mandates securely and efficiently while enabling staff to access the data when and how they need it.</span>[/iconlist_item][iconlist_item type=\"image\" class=\"aligncenter shadow wpb_animate_when_almost_visible fadeIn delay-3\" css=\".vc_custom_1540521656454{padding-right: 10% !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;padding-left: 10% !important;background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.05) !important;*background-color: rgb(255,255,255) !important;border-radius: 5px !important;}\"]\r\n<h6><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Office mobility</span></h6>\r\n<span style=\"color: #9b9aad;\">We help clients create secure applications and remote user experiences in a reliable and secure network for a mobile workforce that can extend to multiple bank branches and offsite contractors.</span>[/iconlist_item][iconlist_item type=\"image\" class=\"aligncenter shadow wpb_animate_when_almost_visible fadeIn delay-4\" css=\".vc_custom_1540521667182{padding-right: 10% !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;padding-left: 10% !important;background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.05) !important;*background-color: rgb(255,255,255) !important;border-radius: 5px !important;}\"]\r\n<h6><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Application development</span></h6>\r\n<span style=\"color: #9b9aad;\">By partnering with us. From the beginning, our managed IT support works within a set budget so our clients get exactly what their business needs without end of month surprises.</span>[/iconlist_item][/iconlist][vc_empty_space height=\"10px\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 15px;\">Stop wasting time and money on technology. <a href=\"http://portal.munihuaura.gob.pe/contact-us/\">Let’s get started</a></p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_section full_width=\"stretch_row\" el_id=\"delivery\" css=\".vc_custom_1536549384735{padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 80px !important;}\"][vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"Delivery\" font_container=\"tag:h6|font_size:10px|text_align:center|color:%23627792\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" el_class=\"style1\"][vc_empty_space height=\"6px\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Transform your technology by focusing on 3 key areas\" font_container=\"tag:h3|text_align:center\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][vc_empty_space height=\"60px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][iconlist icon_size=\"large\"][iconlist_item type=\"image\" icon_image=\"1293\" class=\"wpb_animate_when_almost_visible fadeIn delay-1\"]\r\n<h4>Data transformation</h4>\r\nAccelerate “Data-to-Insight-to-Action” cycle, by consuming offerings like Data-as-a-Service and Reporting-as-a-Service.[/iconlist_item][iconlist_item type=\"image\" icon_image=\"1294\" class=\"wpb_animate_when_almost_visible fadeIn delay-2\"]\r\n<h4>Digital enablement</h4>\r\nDrive key business outcomes, using the full service digital stack – Mosaic, Digital Jedis, and human-centered design experience.[/iconlist_item][iconlist_item type=\"image\" icon_image=\"1295\" class=\"wpb_animate_when_almost_visible fadeIn delay-3\"]\r\n<h4>Innovation partnership</h4>\r\nAdopt a collaborative approach to innovation, by leveraging innovation labs, future financial ecosystems, alliances &amp; partners.[/iconlist_item][/iconlist][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" gap=\"35\" content_placement=\"middle\" css=\".vc_custom_1536551609907{padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 60px !important;background-color: #f3f6f9 !important;}\" el_id=\"expertise\"][vc_column css_animation=\"fadeIn\" width=\"1/2\" el_class=\"delay-1\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Expertise\" font_container=\"tag:h6|font_size:10px|text_align:left|color:%23627792\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" el_class=\"style1\"][vc_empty_space height=\"6px\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Our banking expertise\" font_container=\"tag:h3|text_align:left\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][vc_empty_space height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]NanoSoft is a joint venture between Linethemes and Themeforest. Our experts have deep knowledge about the complexities of the banking industry, and know how to deploy digital technology to transform banks’ operations.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"50px\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" offset=\"vc_col-xs-6\"][counter type=\"image\" value=\"300\" duration=\"1000\" title=\"Financial services firms worldwide\" suffix=\"+\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" offset=\"vc_col-xs-6\"][counter type=\"image\" value=\"7\" duration=\"1000\" title=\"The top largest banks worldwide.\" suffix=\"/10\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_empty_space height=\"20px\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"649\" img_size=\"1170x700\" style=\"vc_box_shadow\" css_animation=\"fadeInRight\"][vc_empty_space height=\"20px\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_section css_animation=\"none\" css=\".vc_custom_1536567268962{padding-top: 80px !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\" el_id=\"case\"][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Customers stories\" font_container=\"tag:h6|font_size:10px|text_align:center\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" el_class=\"style1\"][vc_empty_space height=\"6px\"][elements_carousel items=\"1\" autoplay=\"no\" controls=\"pagination\" autoplay_speed=\"5000\" slide_speed=\"200\" pagination_speed=\"200\" rewind_speed=\"200\" tablet_items=\"2\" mobile_items=\"1\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"NanoSoft are always accommodating our diverse needs and we feel like they are a part of our company rather than an external supplier. <cite>- John H. Bedard, Jr -</cite>\" font_container=\"tag:div|font_size:30px|text_align:center|line_height:1.35em\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"I sleep easier at night knowing the NanoSoft team is in my corner. Supporting my business and keeping my systems in Tip-Top shape. <cite>- Chris Ellison -</cite>\" font_container=\"tag:div|font_size:30px|text_align:center|line_height:1.35em\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][/elements_carousel][vc_empty_space height=\"60px\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][projects mode=\"gri