r business again.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" css_animation=\"fadeIn\" css=\".vc_custom_1537586647389{padding-top: 60px !important;padding-bottom: 60px !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"We take care of your technology\" font_container=\"tag:h3|font_size:26px|text_align:left|color:%23ffffff\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" css_animation=\"none\"][vc_empty_space height=\"20px\"][/vc_column][vc_column css_animation=\"none\" width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"none\"]<span style=\"color: #9b9aad;\">Perhaps it’s time to call in the pros. We’ll whip your IT into shape and set you up with regularly schedule onsite support visits – and we won’t charge any hidden fees to do it. Schedule a FREE consultation today.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][/vc_section][vc_row equal_height=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1537586421722{margin-top: -300px !important;margin-right: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 100px !important;margin-left: 0px !important;background-color: #ffffff !important;}\" el_class=\"shadow\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1537585712300{padding-top: 10% !important;padding-right: 10% !important;padding-bottom: 10% !important;padding-left: 10% !important;background-image: url(http://portal.munihuaura.gob.pe/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/content-bottom-bg.jpg?id=538) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: contain !important;}\" el_class=\"bg-bottom\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Why choose us?\" font_container=\"tag:h3|font_size:26px|text_align:center\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][vc_empty_space height=\"10px\"][vc_column_text]At NanoSoft Technology Solutions, we leverage IT security and automation to help you:[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height=\"40px\"][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1537608626309{padding-right: 10% !important;padding-left: 10% !important;}\"][vc_column_inner][iconlist icon_size=\"small\"][i