dth: 7px !important;border-top-color: #ff4b36 !important;border-top-style: solid !important;}\" class=\"hover2 wpb_animate_when_almost_visible fadeIn delay-1\"]\r\n<h5>Mission and vision</h5>\r\nTo be the global leader in IT services and support. Building on our technologies, competencies and customer interests, and creating value for our stakeholders and customers.\r\n<a class=\"link\" href=\"http://portal.munihuaura.gob.pe/mission-vision-and-values/\">Learn more</a>[/iconlist_item][iconlist_item type=\"image\" css=\".vc_custom_1537860631853{border-top-width: 7px !important;border-top-color: #ff4b36 !important;border-top-style: solid !important;}\" class=\"hover2 wpb_animate_when_almost_visible fadeIn delay-2\"]\r\n<h5>Our challenges</h5>\r\nFrom small to large, traditional to technology driven, we are proud to help customers of all sizes and verticals accomplish their goals. Discover our case studies.\r\n<a class=\"link\" href=\"http://portal.munihuaura.gob.pe/case-studies/\">Learn more</a>[/iconlist_item][iconlist_item type=\"image\" css=\".vc_custom_1539849233827{border-top-width: 7px !important;border-top-color: #ff4b36 !important;border-top-style: solid !important;}\" class=\"hover2 wpb_animate_when_almost_visible fadeIn delay-3\"]\r\n<h5>Technology partners</h5>\r\nOne of NanoSoft\'s defining principles is to be vendor-neutral in everything that we do. We do, however, still rely on leading technology partners to provide products and solutions.\r\n<a class=\"link\" href=\"http://portal.munihuaura.gob.pe/why-choose-us/\">Learn more</a>[/iconlist_item][iconlist_item type=\"image\" css=\".vc_custom_1537860646583{border-top-width: 7px !important;border-top-color: #ff4b36 !important;border-top-style: solid !important;}\" class=\"hover2 wpb_animate_when_almost_visible fadeIn delay-4\"]\r\n<h5>Meet the our team</h5>\r\nHighly experienced management team have brought together a group of passionate engineers to provide you with the reliable and secure technology platform.\r\n<a class=\"link\" href=\"http://portal.munihuaura.gob.pe/leadership-team/\">Learn more</a>[/iconlist_item][iconlist_item type=\"image\" css=\".vc_custom_1539849241686{border-top-width: 7px !important;border-top-color: #ff4b36 !important;border-top-style: solid !important;}\" class=\"hover2 wpb_animate_when_almost_visible fadeIn delay-5\"]\r\n<h5>Careers with us</h5>\r\nOur people are the heart of our operations, which is why we’re fanatical about finding the brightest problem solvers in the IT industry, and giving them a great place to make a difference.\r\n<a class=\"link\" href=\"http://portal.munihuaura.gob.pe/careers/\">Learn more</a>[/iconlist_item][/iconlist][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_section full_width=\"stretch_row\" css_animation=\"none\" css=\".vc_custom_1537844343760{padding-top: 80px !important;padding-bottom: 10px !important;background-color: #231834 !important;}\"][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/12\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"5/6\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Why choose us\" font_container=\"tag:h6|font_size:10px|text_align:center|color:%231dc2ef\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" el_class=\"style1\"][vc_empty_space height=\"6px\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Here are 4 reasons why you should choose us\" font_container=\"tag:h3|text_align:center|color:%23ffffff\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\"][vc_empty_space height=\"60px\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/12\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css_animation=\"none\"][vc_column][iconlist][iconlist_item type=\"image\" class=\"aligncenter shadow wpb_animate_when_almost_visible fadeIn delay-1\" css=\".vc_custom_1540520208040{padding-right: 10% !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;padding-left: 10% !important;background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.05) !important;*background-color: rgb(255,255,255) !important;border-radius: 5px !important;}\"]\r\n<h6><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">People</span></h6>\r\n<span style=\"color: #9b9aad;\">We understand that our people impact the success of our business, and we hire people who are smart.</span>[/iconlist_item][iconlist_item type=\"image\" class=\"aligncenter shadow wpb_animate_when_almost_visible fadeIn delay-2\" css=\".vc_custom_1540520218699{padding-right: 10% !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;padding-left: 10% !important;background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.05) !important;*background-color: rgb(255,255,255) !important;border-radius: 5px !important;}\"]\r\n<h6><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Customer services</span></h6>\r\n<span style=\"color: #9b9aad;\">We strive to provide superior customer service and ensure that every client is completely satisfied with our work.</span>[/iconlist_item][iconlist_item type=\"image\" class=\"aligncenter shadow wpb_animate_when_almost_visible fadeIn delay-3\" css=\".vc_custom_1540520229218{padding-right: 10% !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;padding-left: 10% !important;background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.05) !important;*background-color: rgb(255,255,255) !important;border-radius: 5px !important;}\"]\r\n<h6><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Support</span></h6>\r\n<span style=\"color: #9b9aad;\">Our engineers are trustworthy, dedicated and experienced and will go the extra mile to solve your IT issues.</span>[/iconlist_item][iconlist_item type=\"image\" class=\"aligncenter shadow wpb_animate_when_almost_visible fadeIn delay-4\" css=\".vc_custom_1540520239540{padding-right: 10% !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;padding-left: 10% !important;background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.05) !important;*background-color: rgb(255,255,255) !important;border-radius: 5px !important;}\"]\r\n<h6><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Quality</span></h6>\r\n<span style=\"color: #9b9aad;\">We are committed to deliver outstanding, cutting edge IT solutions that add real value that goes beyond.</span>[/iconlist_item][/iconlist][vc_empty_space height=\"20px\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 15px;\">Stop wasting time and money on technology. <a href=\"http://portal.munihuaura.g